quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"Tuma nde ge…óal neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yim…ìe maa …ìen no soo∆¥ira …óum"
  43,58,"…ìe wi'i: \"Ko rewetee…ói amen …óin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, kaa ko kanko?\" ∆Åe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wanaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko …ìe yim…ìe sa…ótu…ìe wennje"
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaali, si wanaa jeyaa…óo mo Men neemini e mun, Men wa…ói mo misal woannde …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen"
  43,60,"Si Men haajuno, Men wa…ótitirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi"
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wata on sikkito fii maggal. Jokkee lam, ko …óum woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,62,"Wata seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o ga√±o mon …ìanngu…óo"
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e …ìanngu…ói …óin, o maaki: \"Gom…óii mi ardanii on e √±ee√±al, e no mi …ìannginirana on yoga e ko luutondir…óon e muu…óum. Haray hulee Allah, …óofto…óon mi"
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Rewee Mo. Ko …óum woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,65,"Feddeeji …óin luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii …ìen yeddu…ìe, immorde e lepte √±alaande muusu…óe"
  43,66,"Hara …ìe habbi si wanaa nde Darngal ngal ardata …ìe e juhal, hara …ìe so'aa anndude"
  43,67,"Weldu…ìe …ìen, nden √±alnde, yoga ma…ì…ìe ko ayroo…ìe yoga; si wanaa gom…óum…ìe …ìen"